{{\bf E}|X|^k \leq C}
 \displaystyle {\bf P}(|X| \geq \lambda) \leq C \lambda^{-k}, \ \ \ \ \ (23) 
 \displaystyle \lim_{\lambda \rightarrow \infty} \lambda^k {\bf P}(|X| \geq \lambda) = 0. \ \ \ \ \ (24)
{\Large\chi}_{|X|\ge\lambda}|X|^k\le|X|^k
\lim\limits_{\lambda\to\infty}{\Large\chi}_{|X|\ge\lambda}|X|^k=0
 \begin{align} \mathrm{Pr(|X|\ge\lambda)} &=\int_{|X|\ge\lambda}\,\mathrm{d}\mu\\ &\le\lambda^{-k}\int_{|X|\ge\lambda}|X|^k\,\mathrm{d}\mu \end{align} 
 \begin{align} \lambda^k\,\mathrm{Pr(|X|\ge\lambda)} &\le\int_{|X|\ge\lambda}|X|^k\,\mathrm{d}\mu\\ &=\int{\Large\chi}_{|X|\ge\lambda}|X|^k\,\mathrm{d}\mu\\ \end{align} 
 \lim_{\lambda\to\infty}\int{\Large\chi}_{|X|\ge\lambda}|X|^k\,\mathrm{d}\mu=0 
 \lim_{\lambda\to\infty}\lambda^k\,\mathrm{Pr(|X|\ge\lambda)}=0 
